kzRUGlov9gv6H-eBsn_tAA">Thôi Đồ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/S%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-058/poem-z3M3tPiLwUn8v8hY-DcVow">Sơn cư bách vịnh kỳ 058 - 山居百詠其五十八</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-jnvtlp5PrNS3FoOBBGt7-w">Tông Bản thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/T%C3%A1i-ho%E1%BA%A1-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Minh-qu%E1%BB%91c-s%E1%BB%A9-D%C6%B0-Qu%C3%BD-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-9JqBdSa2y_PQmwq2On6Arg">Tái hoạ Đại Minh quốc sứ Dư Quý kỳ 2 - 再和大明國使余貴其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/author-ZuzXfGup2XR6D9EtGGYzeQ">Phạm Sư Mạnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Thanh-th%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-hMuTjtWDPO1xJMpVMkos3Q">Thanh thạch - 青石</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Thi%C3%AAn-Du/Tu%C3%BD-ca-h%C3%A0nh/poem-6y9rj-YrWsH2nTdU8zPseA">Tuý ca hành - 醉歌行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Thi%C3%AAn-Du/author-t5zNl0R6g-15oc9Dd33Eqg">Hồ Thiên Du</a>)<br></div>	</div>
